'=for ref

The regular Bessel function of the first kind, J_n
.
This takes a second int argument which gives the order
of the function required.
');

doco( qw/bessyn/,
'=for ref

The regular Bessel function of the first kind, Y_n
.
This takes a second int argument which gives the order
of the function required.
');

